This paper deals with communication protocols and game theory, which are closely related to information theory (cs.IT) and game theory (cs.GT). The paper also discusses the concept of optimal decoding, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the paper's focus on coordination and stability is relevant to control systems (cs.SY).
